description:
How do you stage $5 million dollars for a production shoot in just two days? You crumple it. Every. Single. Bill. In this episode of *Inside the Beast*, we dive into the production design and team coordination required to prep @MrBeast's large scale challenges and money giveaways. At any given time, Slack workflows route requests for everything from Starlink internet in the wilderness to 20 people needed overnight to build a $5 million pyramid of cash. Managing a team of people on repetitive, high-speed tasks requires the lightning-fast communication of @Slackhq. 

 Peak into the Command Center: Learn more about how MrBeast uses Slack to turn his ideas into actions: https://slack.com/lp/mrbeast 

 Watch more episodes from Inside the Beast: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLnobS_RgN7JZAhVg871pjR1varMRLMprh
